Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}记忆之扉敞开的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:38.88,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}你想一同聆听
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:43.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\blur1}我便倾诉于你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:52.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}啊 虽然这般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}重要的回忆也会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:59.53,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}被时间之沙掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:03.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而变得暧昧不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:10.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}说着「命运」这词是如此廉价
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:14.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而与我一同开怀大笑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:20.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}又是否是我生命中的罗密欧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:25.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}大家 一定会将自己的珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:28.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}逐渐忘却在心的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}与你的一分一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:35.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使只有一瞬 也请留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:39.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使成为无法集齐的拼图
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:43.07,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}那无法寻觅的最后一片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:46.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}记忆之扉敞开的声音
